{"tid":486220,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[10月新番]奇諾之旅 -the Beautiful World- the Animated Series 第9話","createTime":"2017-12-01T15:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T06:41:18.000Z","uid":3020,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0d9cdb5842ccd6291174e2cb1f82bb96e1d682db","tid":486220,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T15:50:49.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n簡介<br />\n年輕的旅行者「奇諾」（Kino）騎著他那會說話的摩托車漢密斯（Hermes）到各個國家旅行，在每個國家奇諾都只停留三天，在她體會了該國家人民的文化、風俗之後，她便離開並前往另一個國家&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JWpDTFm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJWpDTFm.png&h=14aff999&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSTAFF<br />\n原作：時雨澤惠一<br />\n監督：田口智久<br />\n製作：Lerche<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nCAST<br />\n奇諾　：悠木碧<br />\n漢密斯：齊藤壯馬<br />\n西茲　：梅原裕一郎<br />\n陸　　：松田健一郎<br />\n蒂　　：佐倉綾音<br />\n師父　：Lynn<br />\n夥伴　：興津和幸<br />\n<br />\n公式<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.kinonotabi-anime.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kinonotabi-anime.com%2F&d=j5%2B4f%2FOYAeE0ffvFxM8fmW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=e2cd6d0d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.kinonotabi-anime.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nキノの旅 -the Beautiful World- the Animated Series 第9話 「いろいろな国」<br />\n<a href=\"http://himado.in/418347\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhimado.in%2F418347&d=j5%2B4f%2FOYAeE0ffvFxM8fmW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=3db522e7\" target=\"_blank\">http://himado.in/418347</a><br />\n<br />\n線上<br />\n<a href=\"http://myself-bbs.com/thread-43167-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyself-bbs.com%2Fthread-43167-1-1.html&d=j5%2B4f%2FOYAeE0ffvFxM8fmW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=d80db758\" target=\"_blank\">http://myself-bbs.com/thread-43167-1-1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"87537180d86ce92bfc29c67452609c9ce154340d","tid":486220,"uid":14404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201