":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T19:28:57.000Z","msg":"笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個ED係後記之國, 好神<br />\n想問煮野食個個國家, 我睇個個字幕組寫住注意黃色衣服係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後有兩碟唔同既炸雞但都係叫奇諾, 有兩個奇諾?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f30e86b01a4af9a9429852608b0555c3e73d38","tid":486220,"uid":23086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T22:28:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個ED係後記之國, 好神<br />\n想問煮野食個個國家, 我睇個個字幕組寫住注意黃色衣服係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後有兩碟唔同既炸雞但都係叫奇諾, 有兩個奇諾?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試食個個就正版廚神"},{"pid":"1c6dd2d07b2fda9eb813e98f7b245ecf1e1c7bd3","tid":486220,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T00:24:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解師傅咁cls架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n師傳嗰邊做野多數錢字行頭,夠膽打劫佢,唔洗死都算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605e23baadf4a44e89ceca9c008990e02719e305","tid":486220,"uid":63414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:34:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個ED係後記之國, 好神<br />\n想問煮野食個個國家, 我睇個個字幕組寫住注意黃色衣服係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後有兩碟唔同既炸雞但都係叫奇諾, 有兩個奇諾?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n天才"},{"pid":"104d153cf3cebf01b0c28b0f72e1be469b8a7b8b","tid":486220,"uid":72590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:37:51.000Z","msg":"好彩平時都聽埋ed，今集都幾多個單元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3bbfc5f56c34fc303b919a50f70695d81092c94","tid":486220,"uid":143023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T15:30:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個ED係後記之國, 好神<br />\n想問煮野食個個國家, 我睇個個字幕組寫住注意黃色衣服係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後有兩碟唔同既炸雞但都係叫奇諾, 有兩個奇諾?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試食個個就正版廚神</blockquote><br />\n唔明啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9317c6b06dc1b9c2141099c5cab1e85bc9b85e2","tid":486220,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T00:43:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個ED係後記之國, 好神<br />\n想問煮野食個個國家, 我睇個個字幕組寫住注意黃色衣服係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後有兩碟唔同既炸雞但都係叫奇諾, 有兩個奇諾?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試食個個就正版廚神</blockquote><br />\n唔明啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有一個流浪廚神就快黎到呢個國家傳言,呢間餐廳既廚師就想扮到認唔出佢咁請流浪廚神煮兩味<br />\n然後奇諾早過流浪廚神到先,咁啱兩人既衣著相似,班廚師就誤會奇諾就係廚神,請佢煮野食,但實際上奇諾煮野係差到仆街<br />\n班廚師覺得既然係廚神整既就一定好食,明明唔好食都呃自己係好食,重當係招牌菜咁賣<br />\n後來流浪廚神黎到,食過之後覺得頂唔順,就自己改良左呢道菜<br />\n一開始班廚師覺得佢好離譜,竟然夠膽改左廚神(奇諾)菜式,但食落又真係好食,所以最後就兩種都拎去賣"},{"pid":"0b2c817924cf80b85853bcaa8a79b1ad70082ac5","tid":486220,"uid":143023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T02:52:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個ED係後記之國, 好神<br />\n想問煮野食個個國家, 我睇個個字幕組寫住注意黃色衣服係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後有兩碟唔同既炸雞但都係叫奇諾, 有兩個奇諾?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試食個個就正版廚神</blockquote><br />\n唔明啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有一個流浪廚神就快黎到呢個國家傳言,呢間餐廳既廚師就想扮到認唔出佢咁請流浪廚神煮兩味<br />\n然後奇諾早過流浪廚神到先,咁啱兩人既衣著相似,班廚師就誤會奇諾就係廚神,請佢煮野食,但實際上奇諾煮野係差到仆街<br />\n班廚師覺得既然係廚神整既就一定好食,明明唔好食都呃自己係好食,重當係招牌菜咁賣<br />\n後來流浪廚神黎到,食過之後覺得頂唔順,就自己改良左呢道菜<br />\n一開始班廚師覺得佢好離譜,竟然夠膽改左廚神(奇諾)菜式,但食落又真係好食,所以最後就兩種都拎去賣</blockquote><br />\n係啵 睇番試食到暈個個都係 黃色大褸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528800d05664bc4e59acd3196e79d61bc71eb97d","tid":486220,"uid":56657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T14:30:06.000Z","msg":"呢套笑死<br />\n好多單元,又跳下跳下咁<br />\n有少少舊版既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好想知個個美好回憶之國係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca679eaf1e70009855d22dae817661b47c5bfe55","tid":486220,"uid":2380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T14:35:42.000Z","msg":"點解推返第9集咁得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65bcd48cc5e25d7dfee8390fc0bb1bc88b8ed5a","tid":486220,"uid":28916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T05:02:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解推返第9集咁得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如直接開集中討論區好過啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fe0da77df59c77679c96797994f09a1e0b110bc","tid":486220,"uid":14404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T05:41:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解推返第9集咁得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如直接開集中討論區好過啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一早講左咁冷唔應該分集開<br />\n依家都就完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d1b932228389617130de252facccb3e01f4c9f","tid":486220,"u